project.name: Hero: Molly Tuttle: From Rancid Covers to Grammy Gold

data.label: Style
data.name: w33s3 Dark
data.description: Dark, moody atmosphere with high contrast lighting. Cinematic composition with neon accent colors against deep blacks. Professional photography feel, dramatic shadows, rich color depth. Modern minimalist aesthetic, no text or watermarks.

data.label: Action
data.content: A woman's hands on an acoustic guitar, flatpicking with intensity. Split composition: one side warm amber stage lights of a bluegrass venue, other side green punk show lighting. Film grain texture. No face visible, focus on the guitar and the contrast between two musical worlds merging.
